---
title: Agent Design Lifecycle State Machine
---
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> DRAFT : Queen builds / Evolution regenerates

    DRAFT --> CANDIDATE : GraphSpec.validate() clean
    note right of DRAFT : Graph may be incomplete\nor structurally invalid

    CANDIDATE --> VALIDATED : ≥1 session success=True
    CANDIDATE --> ARCHIVED : Abandoned

    note right of CANDIDATE : Built, awaiting\nexecution evidence

    VALIDATED --> PROMOTED : User stars / approves
    note right of VALIDATED : Automated gate passed\nAwaiting human judgment

    PROMOTED --> ARCHIVED : Superseded by newer PROMOTED
    note right of PROMOTED : "The good version"\nIntegrity-checksummed

    note right of ARCHIVED : Preserved for rollback\nNever deleted

    ARCHIVED --> [*]
